.TH LOA 1 "2026-03-15" "Library Of Alexandria" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
loa \- command index for Library Of Alexandria
.SH SYNOPSIS
Use these commands inside the interactive prompt:
.br
alexandria> <command>
.SH DESCRIPTION
This page lists all available commands and where to find their dedicated man pages.
.SH COMMAND MANUALS
.TP
\fBadd\fR
Interactively add a new item (book or sheet music) to your library (see \fBloa-add.1\fR)
.TP
\fBedit\fR
Edit fields of an item selected by reference (see \fBloa-edit.1\fR)
.TP
\fBdetails\fR
Show one item in a structured detail view (see \fBloa-details.1\fR)
.TP
\fBlist\fR
Show all items (see \fBloa-list.1\fR)
.TP
\fBlist full\fR
Show full table with all item columns (see \fBloa-list-full.1\fR)
.TP
\fBlist read\fR
Show only read items (see \fBloa-list-read.1\fR)
.TP
\fBlist unread\fR
Show only unread items (see \fBloa-list-unread.1\fR)
.TP
\fBlist sheet\fR
Show only sheet music items (see \fBloa-list-sheet.1\fR)
.TP
\fBlist genre <name>\fR
Show items by exact genre name (see \fBloa-list-genre.1\fR)
.TP
\fBlist language <name>\fR
Show items by exact language value (see \fBloa-list-language.1\fR)
.TP
\fBlist instrument <name>\fR
Show sheet music by instrumentation (see \fBloa-list-instrument.1\fR)
.TP
\fBlist tag <name>\fR
Show items by tag (see \fBloa-list-tag.1\fR)
.TP
\fBsort by <field>\fR
Sort items by a supported field (see \fBloa-sort-by.1\fR)
.TP
\fBfind title\fR
Search items by title substring (see \fBloa-find-title.1\fR)
.TP
\fBfind author\fR
Search items by author substring (see \fBloa-find-author.1\fR)
.TP
\fBfind composer\fR
Search sheet music by composer substring (see \fBloa-find-composer.1\fR)
.TP
\fBauthors\fR
Show all authors with counts and top genres/tags (see \fBloa-authors.1\fR)
.TP
\fBfind notes\fR
Search full-text notes (see \fBloa-find-notes.1\fR)
.TP
\fBcheck\fR
Show one item by reference (see \fBloa-check.1\fR)
.TP
\fBremove\fR
Delete an item by reference (see \fBloa-remove.1\fR)
.TP
\fBmark read\fR
Mark an item as read (see \fBloa-mark-read.1\fR)
.TP
\fBmark unread\fR
Mark an item as unread (see \fBloa-mark-unread.1\fR)
.TP
\fBnotes\fR
Update notes for an item (see \fBloa-notes.1\fR)
.TP
\fBtag add\fR
Add tags to an item (see \fBloa-tag-add.1\fR)
.TP
\fBtag remove\fR
Remove tags from an item (see \fBloa-tag-remove.1\fR)
.TP
\fBtag set\fR
Replace all tags on an item (see \fBloa-tag-set.1\fR)
.TP
\fBtag clear\fR
Clear all tags on an item (see \fBloa-tag-clear.1\fR)
.TP
\fBrate\fR
Set or clear rating (1-5) (see \fBloa-rate.1\fR)
.TP
\fBprogress\fR
Set current page progress (see \fBloa-progress.1\fR)
.TP
\fBlanguage\fR
Set language of an item (see \fBloa-language.1\fR)
.TP
\fBlocation\fR
Set physical location of an item (see \fBloa-location.1\fR)
.TP
\fBpractice\fR
Set practice status for a sheet music entry (see \fBloa-practice.1\fR)
.TP
\fBreading add\fR
Add an item to reading list (see \fBloa-reading-add.1\fR)
.TP
\fBreading list\fR
Show reading list books (see \fBloa-reading-list.1\fR)
.TP
\fBreading remove\fR
Remove an item from reading list (see \fBloa-reading-remove.1\fR)
.TP
\fBreading smart preview [count]\fR
Preview recommendations based on interests (see \fBloa-reading-smart-preview.1\fR)
.TP
\fBreading smart generate [count]\fR
Replace reading list with recommendations (see \fBloa-reading-smart-generate.1\fR)
.TP
\fBreading smart append [count]\fR
Append recommendations to reading list (see \fBloa-reading-smart-append.1\fR)
.TP
\fBinterests set\fR
Configure smart recommendation interests (see \fBloa-interests-set.1\fR)
.TP
\fBinterests show\fR
Show smart recommendation interests (see \fBloa-interests-show.1\fR)
.TP
\fBinterests clear\fR
Reset smart recommendation interests (see \fBloa-interests-clear.1\fR)
.TP
\fBsmart add\fR
Create or update a smart list (see \fBloa-smart-add.1\fR)
.TP
\fBsmart list\fR
List saved smart lists (see \fBloa-smart-list.1\fR)
.TP
\fBsmart run\fR
Run a smart list (see \fBloa-smart-run.1\fR)
.TP
\fBsmart remove\fR
Delete a smart list (see \fBloa-smart-remove.1\fR)
.TP
\fBgoal show\fR
Display reading goals and progress (see \fBloa-goal-show.1\fR)
.TP
\fBgoal set monthly\fR
Set monthly reading target (see \fBloa-goal-set-monthly.1\fR)
.TP
\fBgoal set yearly\fR
Set yearly reading target (see \fBloa-goal-set-yearly.1\fR)
.TP
\fBgoal clear monthly\fR
Clear monthly reading goal (see \fBloa-goal-clear-monthly.1\fR)
.TP
\fBgoal clear yearly\fR
Clear yearly reading goal (see \fBloa-goal-clear-yearly.1\fR)
.TP
\fBstats\fR
Show aggregate library statistics (see \fBloa-stats.1\fR)
.TP
\fBsheet stats\fR
Show sheet-music-specific statistics (see \fBloa-sheet-stats.1\fR)
.TP
\fBbackup\fR
Create timestamped JSON backup (see \fBloa-backup.1\fR)
.TP
\fBrestore\fR
Restore library from JSON backup/export (see \fBloa-restore.1\fR)
.TP
\fBexport\fR
Export data as JSON or CSV (see \fBloa-export.1\fR)
.TP
\fBexport obsidian\fR
Export markdown notes for an Obsidian vault (see \fBloa-export-obsidian.1\fR)
.TP
\fBobsidian\fR
Show configured Obsidian vault and usage hints (see \fBloa-obsidian.1\fR)
.TP
\fBobsidian sync\fR
Sync managed Alexandria notes into an Obsidian vault (see \fBloa-obsidian-sync.1\fR)
.TP
\fBobsidian doctor\fR
Validate Obsidian vault path, write access, and required folders (see \fBloa-obsidian-doctor.1\fR)
.TP
\fBobsidian open\fR
Open Obsidian vault or a specific managed note without exiting the CLI (see \fBloa-obsidian-open.1\fR)
.TP
\fBimport\fR
Import items from JSON or CSV (see \fBloa-import.1\fR)
.TP
\fBman\fR
Show bundled command manual pages from inside the app (see \fBloa-man.1\fR)
.TP
\fBcompact\fR
Toggle compact table mode (see \fBloa-compact.1\fR)
.TP
\fBtheme\fR
Show, switch, and personalize colors (see \fBloa-theme.1\fR)
.TP
\fBundo\fR
Revert the latest change (see \fBloa-undo.1\fR)
.TP
\fBhistory\fR
Show typed command history (see \fBloa-history.1\fR)
.TP
\fBhelp\fR
Show built-in command list (see \fBloa-help.1\fR)
.TP
\fBquit\fR
Exit the application (see \fBloa-quit.1\fR)
.SH SEE ALSO
